'''瑪麗·法蘭西絲·「德琵」·雷諾'''（{{lang-en|'''Mary Frances "Debbie" Reynolds'''}}，{{bd|1932年|4月1日|2016年|12月28日|Reynolds, Debbie}}），美國女演員，1952年擔演電影《[[萬花嬉春|萬花嬉春]]》女主角成名。一生中曾三度結婚，與著名藝人[[艾迪·費雪|艾迪·費雪]]第一次婚姻裡所生的女兒[[嘉莉·費雪|嘉莉·費雪]]則以演出《[[星際大戰|星際大戰]]》系列著名。曾在[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆奧斯卡金像獎]]獲得[[简·赫尔索特人道精神奖|简·赫尔索特人道精神奖]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/08/governors-awards-2015-spike-lee-debbie-reynolds-gena-rowlands-1201507536/ |title=Governors Awards: Spike Lee, Debbie Reynolds & Gena Rowlands Get 2015 Honors |access-date=2016-12-30 |archive-date=2016-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160224115116/http://deadline.com/2015/08/governors-awards-2015-spike-lee-debbie-reynolds-gena-rowlands-1201507536/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年 ===
雷諾有[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]，[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]和[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]血統。

=== 逝世 ===
2016年12月23日，雷諾的女兒-—同時為演員與作家的[[嘉莉·費雪|嘉莉·費雪]]，在搭機由倫敦前往[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]途中，突然心臟病發。耶誕節當天，雷諾曾發布費雪情況穩定的訊息。然而，費雪在12月27日病逝，享壽60歲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/27/movies/carrie-fisher-dead-star-wars-princess-leia.html?_r=0|first=Dave|last=Itzkoff|title=Carrie Fisher, Child of Hollywood and 'Star Wars' Royalty, Dies at 60|publisher=''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''|date=December 27, 2016|accessdate=December 27, 2016|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120204920/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/27/movies/carrie-fisher-dead-star-wars-princess-leia.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

翌日（12月28日），雷諾在兒子家中突然中風，因情況危急住進洛杉磯的{{tsl|en|Cedars-Sinai Medical Center|錫安山醫學中心}}，並於當日午後過世<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/entertainment/debbie-reynolds-dead-1.3914744 |title=Actress Debbie Reynolds dead at 84 |author=The Associated Press<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=December 28, 2016 |website=CBC News |publisher=CBC |access-date=December 28, 2016 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108120049/https://www.cbc.ca/news/entertainment/debbie-reynolds-dead-1.3914744 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="auto">{{cite news |last=Rubin |first=Joel |date=December 28, 2016 |title=Debbie Reynolds rushed to the hospital after falling ill; condition unknown |url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-debbie-reynolds-ill-20161228-story.html |newspaper=LA Times |location=Los Angeles |access-date=December 28, 2016 |archive-date=2020-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206020809/https://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-debbie-reynolds-ill-20161228-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/debbie-reynolds-dead-dies-carrie-fisher-mother-1201949432/ |title=Debbie Reynolds Dead at 84 |last=Dagan |first=Carmel |date=December 28, 2016 |website=Variety |publisher=Variety |access-date=December 28, 2016 |archive-date=2021-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224052902/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/debbie-reynolds-dead-dies-carrie-fisher-mother-1201949432/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/debbie-reynolds-dead-dies-carrie-fisher-mother-1201949432/|title=Debbie Reynolds, "Singin' in the Rain" Star and Carrie Fisher’s Mother, Dies at 84|last=Dagan|first=Carmel|date=December 28, 2016|website=Variety|publisher=Variety|access-date=December 28, 2016|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224052902/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/debbie-reynolds-dead-dies-carrie-fisher-mother-1201949432/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

雷諾遺屬包含其子陶德·費雪及外孫女[[比莉·洛爾德|比莉·洛爾德]]。陶德·費雪已對外確認死因為中風，並表示雷諾面對女兒的猝逝所帶來的壓力，可能是導致她中風的原因。報載「雷諾曾說，她相當思念女兒嘉莉，並想隨她而去」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/28/movies/debbie-reynolds-dead.html|title=Debbie Reynolds, Wholesome Ingénue in 1950s Films, Dies at 84|date=December 29, 2016|work=The New York Times|access-date=2016-12-29|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210045141/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/28/movies/debbie-reynolds-dead.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

